evel-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/6-loi-khuyen-de-tao-su-hung-thu-cho-lop-hoc\/#khoi_dong_voi_nhung_dieu_bi_an\" >Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ed \u1ea9n<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/6-loi-khuyen-de-tao-su-hung-thu-cho-lop-hoc\/#lop_hoc_dao_nguoc_co_the_rat_hieu_qua\" >L\u1edbp h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ea3o ng\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/6-loi-khuyen-de-tao-su-hung-thu-cho-lop-hoc\/#tong_ket_bai_hoc_la_quan_trong\" >T\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/6-loi-khuyen-de-tao-su-hung-thu-cho-lop-hoc\/#hoc_cung_nhau\" >H\u1ecdc c\u00f9ng nhau<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/6-loi-khuyen-de-tao-su-hung-thu-cho-lop-hoc\/#lam_cho_cac_bai_hoc_tro_nen_thu_vi\" >L\u00e0m cho c\u00e1c b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u00fa v\u1ecb<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/6-loi-khuyen-de-tao-su-hung-thu-cho-lop-hoc\/#tan_dung_cong_nghe\" >T\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/6-loi-khuyen-de-tao-su-hung-thu-cho-lop-hoc\/#ket_luan\" >K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<blockquote><p>H\u1ecdc sinh h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n khi h\u1ecd c\u00f3 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa. Thu h\u00fat h\u1ecdc sinh tham gia v\u00e0o tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 l\u00e0m cho l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u00fa v\u1ecb l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi nh\u1edb nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft l\u00e0 l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa trong khi v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n.<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khoi_dong_voi_nhung_dieu_bi_an\"><\/span>Kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ed \u1ea9n<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>H\u00e3y k\u00edch th\u00edch hay l\u00f4i k\u00e9o b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 h\u01a1i v\u00f4 l\u00fd v\u00e0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1, b\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh. B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi g\u00e2y t\u00f2 m\u00f2 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc sinh mong ch\u1edd c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi. H\u00e3y t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho ph\u1ea7n k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecdc sinh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi ban \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf cu\u1ed1i b\u00e0i, k\u1ebft th\u00fac cho m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ea7y t\u00f2 m\u00f2, h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa c\u00f9ng h\u1ecdc sinh c\u1eeda b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11596 size-medium\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/iStock-497892734-1200x800-1-600x400.jpg\" alt=\"6 l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa cho l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc \" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/iStock-497892734-1200x800-1-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/iStock-497892734-1200x800-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/iStock-497892734-1200x800-1.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lop_hoc_dao_nguoc_co_the_rat_hieu_qua\"><\/span>L\u1edbp h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ea3o ng\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho ph\u00e9p h\u1ecdc sinh t\u1ef1 h\u1ecdc \u1edf nh\u00e0, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 chia nh\u1ecf nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc, \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi cho gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc sinh kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 c\u00e1c kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m \u0111ang h\u1ecdc. H\u00e3y cho ph\u00e9p h\u1ecdc sinh l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi h\u1ecd v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u1eddi gian trong l\u1edbp \u0111\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc sinh kh\u00e1c m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a.<\/p>\n<p>Khi xem x\u00e9t c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m cho l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch hay \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m cho l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u00fa v\u1ecb m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i hy sinh nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong_ket_bai_hoc_la_quan_trong\"><\/span>T\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m tra nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc sinh b\u1eb1ng tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i A \u2013 Z. Gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean s\u1ebd vi\u1ebft c\u00e1c ch\u1eef c\u00e1i t\u1eeb A \u2013 Z l\u00ean c\u00e1c t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb. M\u1ed7i t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1eef c\u00e1i. H\u1ecdc sinh\/ gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean s\u1ebd b\u1ed1c m\u1ed9t ch\u1eef c\u00e1i b\u1ea5t k\u00ec. H\u1ecdc sinh ph\u1ea3i t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n l\u1ea1i n\u1ed9i dung b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t t\u1eeb kh\u00f3a li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng ch\u1eef c\u00e1i v\u1eeba b\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady s\u1ebd k\u00edch th\u00edch v\u00e0 l\u00f4i cu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tham gia c\u1ee7a h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft h\u1ecdc sinh trong ti\u1ebft h\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1eebng ch\u1ec9 \u00f4n l\u1ea1i theo \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ea1y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, m\u00e0 h\u00e3y xem x\u00e9t c\u00e1c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea1t thay th\u1ebf kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00edch th\u00edch tr\u00ed nh\u1edb b\u00e0i gi\u1ea3ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"hoc_cung_nhau\"><\/span>H\u1ecdc c\u00f9ng nhau<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>Th\u1eed th\u00e1ch b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp. \u0110\u1eebng ng\u1ea1i kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u1edbi v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc sinh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Cho ph\u00e9p h\u1ecdc sinh th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n. C\u00f9ng nhau kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u00e0 khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lam_cho_cac_bai_hoc_tro_nen_thu_vi\"><\/span>L\u00e0m cho c\u00e1c b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u00fa v\u1ecb<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>Bi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch h\u1ecdc sinh tham gia. C\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ng\u1ed3i trong khi h\u1ecdc sinh d\u1ea1y b\u1ea1n b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc. Cho ph\u00e9p h\u1ecdc sinh ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1eabn nhau v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ea5m \u0111i\u1ec3m cho b\u1ea1n trong c\u00e1c b\u00e0i thuy\u1ebft tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1eebng ng\u1ea1i c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 vui v\u1ebb trong khi v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t.<\/p>\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ea9m quy\u1ec1n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n qu\u00e1 kh\u1eaft khe v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea3 l\u1ecfng m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat, l\u1eafng nghe h\u1ecdc sinh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang. Chia s\u1ebb khi th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 cho ph\u00e9p sinh vi\u00ean chia s\u1ebb kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecdc ho\u1eb7c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. B\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch c\u1edfi m\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 sinh vi\u00ean tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec kh\u00e1c m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn.<\/p>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tan_dung_cong_nghe\"><\/span>T\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>Ng\u00e0y nay b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7; sinh vi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eafm m\u00ecnh trong c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y. Mang c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0o trong l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i. C\u00f3 c\u00e1c nh\u00f3m tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng video v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y tr\u00ean YouTube, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Tivi t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c th\u00f4ng minh, M\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecdc sinh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-11597 size-medium\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/850e77e4-school-class-sitting-cross-legged-using-tablets-700px-600x400.jpg\" alt=\"6 l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa cho l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc \" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/850e77e4-school-class-sitting-cross-legged-using-tablets-700px-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/850e77e4-school-class-sitting-cross-legged-using-tablets-700px.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" \/><\/p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/man-hinh-tuong-tac-thong-minh-inno-itv-ka12-series\/\">M\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c INNO<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/may-chieu-chuyen-dung-danh-cho-giao-duc-inno\/\">M\u00e1y chi\u1ebfu gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c INNO<\/a><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket_luan\"><\/span>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>H\u00e3y th\u1eed v\u00e0 suy ngh\u0129 th\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1o khi n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u trong l\u1edbp. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m cho l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa, cho c\u1ea3 b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh. \u0110\u01b0a ra c\u00e1c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn, thu h\u00fat h\u1ecdc sinh tham gia, m\u1eddi di\u1ec5n gi\u1ea3 kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi, \u0111i h\u1ecdc ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi, \u0111i th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf ho\u1eb7c xem x\u00e9t c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u00fat h\u1ecdc sinh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n<p>Follow ngay Fanpage <a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/innovietnam\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">INNO Vi\u1ec7t Nam !<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>H\u1ecdc sinh h\u1ecdc t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n khi h\u1ecd c\u00f3 h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa. Thu h\u00fat h\u1ecdc sinh tham gia v\u00e0o tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 l\u00e0m cho l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u00fa v\u1ecb l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi nh\u1edb nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":11596,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[66],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-11595","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/11595","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn